<span class="line"><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>关于移除会议室，还做了一个兜底处理：</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">MeetingRoomManager</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token operator">...</span></span>
