<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">draw</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
